<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-23 00:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9631 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r f BC-NETWORTH-PENDER-SFCHR     08-23 1218
