   TIRE-RECALL (Detroit) _ The Firestone tires that have been
failing on Ford Explorer sport utility vehicles have fairly low
weight-carrying capability for a vehicle of the Explorer's size,
particularly at the fairly low inflation pressure recommended by
the Ford Motor Co., publicly available technical specifications for
the tires and the Explorers show. By Keith Bradsher.
