<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-23 11:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9886 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-CPT-NEW-ECON-COLUMN-N     08-23 1040
