<P>
   AIRLINE-STATS _ Decoding the government data tracking airline
delays and late arrivals isn't as bad as enduring an unexpected
cancellation, but it's no trip in first-class, either. The FAA and
DOT both produce sets of numbers that measure the problem very
differently. A look at the meaning behind the stats being widely
cited this summer as evidence the system is failing. (Fonti,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 18.
</P>
<P>
   TAX-BLUES _ WASHINGTON _ Blue Cross &AMP; Blue Shield of Texas Inc.
may be liable for millions of dollars in additional federal taxes
under a precedent-setting U.S. Tax Court ruling. (Moskal, Cox News
Service). 18.
</P>
