 &HT;    
 &HT;    This column moved today:
 &HT;    
 &HT;    BERNARD GLADSTONE'S ``HOME IMPROVEMENT QUESTIONS AND ANSWERS''
for Sun., Sep. 10, 2000, which included:
 &HT;    _An easy way to make sure wallpaper fits exactly around window
frames (comes with illustration).
