<SLUG> BC-LOVE&AMP;SEX-REVIEW-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A WINNER IN `LOVE &AMP; SEX'
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Fact box below) 
Our rating: 3 stars 
By BOB STRAUSS 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
