<HEADLINE>
PATS, CMGI HOPE FOR WINNING TEAM 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (f and s coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By MEG VAILLANCOURT  
 c.2000 The Boston Globe  
 
