   GEORGE W. BUSH: New Orleans, Miami
</P>
<P>
   DICK CHENEY: Medford and Portland, Ore.
</P>
<P>
   AL GORE AND JOSEPH LIEBERMAN: Washington, College Park, Md.
</P>
<P>
   RALPH NADER: Sacramento, Calif.
